The PERFECT stands for PERFormance Effort Calculating Tool. It comprises of
 
1. Script efforts input section.
2. Execution efforts input section and
3. Tool setup efforts input section.
 
Filling in all the input section in "white" fields and clicking on the "Estimate" button would trigger the Estimating engine that 
would provide us the Total effort estimate required in Hours, Man days and Weeks. The final estimate will be stored on Desktop as .pdf file.
 
Built on ~ 2700 + lines of code, sharing the PERFECT for SAP tool so that it can be leveraged by other projects, if they have a need.
 
[Kind Note: The numbers are rounded to the nearest integer. Hence Performance Test Managers and Leads are requested to have 
this in mind while sharing the data with clients]

Supported Operating System: Windows
